overview: You've been asking for another volume in the Bringin' Up The Rear series and today we've got it for you. And boy, is it a good compilation. Twelve hot soldiers giving in and giving up their tight virgin holes for the first time. Breakin' in the newbies is one of the most fun things about my job and my long-time buddy Cole has helped us out a lot in that department. Today we bring you two hours of first timers getting it balls deep ... some of them in agony and others in extreme pleasure. Nonetheless it's the first time for all of them and a great way to catalog these first timers for quick and easy reference in this compilation.
title: Bringing Up the Rear 3
